# Cursor AI Configuration for Portfolio 2026

## Example Files Directory
When building components or features, reference example files from the `.cursor/examples/` directory for:
- Component patterns and structure
- Code style and conventions
- Best practices for this project

## Project Context
This is a React portfolio website built with Vite. Use the example files as templates when creating new components or features.

## Typography
Headings use **Arvo**; load fonts via `src/styles/fonts.css` (imported from `index.css`). Body copy on case-study pages uses **Raleway**; base UI uses **Inter**.

## Example Files Location
Example files are located in: `.cursor/examples/`

Reference these files when:
- Creating new React components
- Setting up data structures
- Implementing styling patterns
- Building portfolio features
